
TrinteJS MVC Bootstrapper

This is the help file for the Express based application bootstrapper.  Parameters marked with * are optional, and are shown with their defaults.

Usage: trinte [command(s)] [argument(s)]

Command format:

trinte                                   : Run the application using the cluster module.
trinte cluster *port=3000                : Run the application using the cluster module.
trinte server *port=3000                 : Run the application as a server.

trinte test                              : Run all tests.
trinte test unit|integration|functional  : Run a particular type of test.

trinte script help *<name>               : This help script, optional script name for additional help.
trinte script <name> *params             : Run a script with <name>, with params.

Available scripts (generators):

create-controller                        : Creates a controller script
create-model *params                     : Creates a model script
create-test                              : Creates a test
create-view *params                      : Creates a view files
generate-all *params                     : Creates a scaffold
help                                     : Show this help

Show help for script example:

$ trinte script help generate-all

Create a scripts examples:

# Creates a scaffold
$ trinte script generate-all Post
$ trinte script generate-all Post published:bool title:string content:string created:date

# Creates a model
$ trinte script create-model User
$ trinte script create-model User active:bool name:string email:string password:string